     * @allow (update) - User with UID 'dKA5w1X5uMZUGAMF5GHrYtA6QB82' can update their own weekly improvement plan.
     * @allow (delete) - User with UID 'dKA5w1X5uMZUGAMF5GHrYtA6QB82' can delete their own weekly improvement plan.
     * @deny (create) - User with UID ' অন্যUID' cannot create a weekly improvement plan for 'dKA5w1X5uMZUGAMF5GHrYtA6QB82'.
     * @deny (get) - User with UID ' অন্যUID' cannot read a weekly improvement plan of 'dKA5w1X5uMZUGAMF5GHrYtA6QB82'.
     * @deny (list) - User with UID ' অন্যUID' cannot list the weekly improvement plans of 'dKA5w1X5uMZUGAMF5GHrYtA6QB82'.
     * @deny (update) - User with UID ' অন্যUID' cannot update a weekly improvement plan of 'dKA5w1X5uMZUGAMF5GHrYtA6QB82'.
     * @deny (delete) - User with UID ' অন্যUID' cannot delete a weekly improvement plan of 'dKA5w1X5uMZUGAMF5GHrYtA6QB82'.
