    /**
     * @description Enforces ownership for monthly summary reports.
     * @path /users/{userId}/monthlySummaries/{monthlySummaryId}
     * @allow (create) - User with UID 'dKA5w1X5uMZUGAMF5GHrYtA6QB82' can create a monthly summary report.
     * @allow (get) - User with UID 'dKA5w1X5uMZUGAMF5GHrYtA6QB82' can read their own monthly summary report.
     * @allow (list) - User with UID 'dKA5w1X5uMZUGAMF5GHrYtA6QB82' can list their own monthly summary reports.
     * @allow (update) - User with UID 'dKA5w1X5uMZUGAMF5GHrYtA6QB82' can update their own monthly summary report.
     * @allow (delete) - User with UID 'dKA5w1X5uMZUGAMF5GHrYtA6QB82' can delete their own monthly summary report.
     * @deny (create) - User with UID ' অন্যUID' cannot create a monthly summary report for 'dKA5w1X5uMZUGAMF5GHrYtA6QB82'.
     * @deny (get) - User with UID ' অন্যUID' cannot read a monthly summary report of 'dKA5w1X5uMZUGAMF5GHrYtA6QB82'.
     * @deny (list) - User with UID ' অন্যUID' cannot list the monthly summary reports of 'dKA5w1X5uMZUGAMF5GHrYtA6QB82'.
     * @deny (update) - User with UID ' অন্যUID' cannot update a monthly summary report of 'dKA5w1X5uMZUGAMF5GHrYtA6QB82'.
